## Current limitations (transparent)
- Literature may be sparse in dev; tier remains conservative. Chromatin may be heuristic unless providers enabled.
- Fusion requires GRCh38 missense coverage; otherwise omitted and labeled.

## Success criteria
- Table renders with rank, confidence, tier, badges, chip values, rationale, and citations; export + provenance present.
- Evidence panel loads without blocking; cohort overlays lift confidence when aligned.
- RUO visible across views; tooltips explain tier/badges and chip thresholds.

